IMPORTANT DISCLAIMERS
Peddock Capital Advisors, LLC ("PCA") is a Registered Investment Advisor ("RIA"), located in the Commonwealth of Massachusetts. PCA provides investment advisory and related services to clients nationally. PCA will maintain all applicable registration and licenses as required by the various states in which PCA conducts business, as applicable. PCA renders individualized responses to persons in a particular state only after complying with all regulatory requirements, or pursuant to an applicable state exemption or exclusion. 
